room_title: Escape room "Escape the Zoo" by I-20 Escape in Ruston
room_description: Those mischievous monkeys are at it again.  They have once again escaped the watchful eye of Harold, their leader, AKA “Dad”.  Not only have they taken Jasper the zookeeper’s personal tools and hidden them around the zoo, they have also managed to lock you up too!  Your mission is to undo the mischief they have caused, find them, and put them back in their own cage before the zoo closes in only 60 minutes.
